700401f-b.title: Bronx: Alexander Avenue - 140th Street (East)
700401f-b.text:
(1)Alexander Avenue, east side, north from East 140th Street.
At the south east corner of Fast 141st Street is the Alexander
Avenue Baptist Church. Beyond that can be seen the spire of
St. Mary's Episcopal Church, at 141st Street.
(2)is north from Fast 141st Street.
(3)shows a closeup of the Alexander Avenue Baptist Church.
P. L. Sperr  View 1: November 14, 1937
No Reproductions  View 2,3 April 29, 1941
